ENIAMsemantics Version 1.0 :
-----------------------

ENIAMsemantics implements semantic processing for ENIAM.

Install
-------

ENIAMsemantics requires OCaml version 4.02.3 compiler
together with Xlib library version 3.2 or later
and ENIAMlexSemantics library version 1.0.

In order to install type:

make install

by default, ENIAM_LCGlexicon is installed in the 'ocamlc -where'/eniam directory.
you can change it by editing the Makefile.

In order to test library type:
make test
./test

In order to print lexicon as pdf file type:
make print_lexicon
./print_lexicon

Both test and print_lexicon require pdflatex installed.

By default ENIAM_LCGlexicon looks for resources in /usr/share/eniam directory.
However this behaviour may be changed by setting end exporting ENIAM_RESOURCE_PATH
environment variable.

